The configuration for fusiondirectory.conf is:

For users

...
      <usertabs>
           ...
           <tab class="zarafaAccount" name="Zarafa" />
           ...
      </usertabs>
...

For groups

...
     <grouptabs>
           ...
           <tab class="zarafagroup" name="Zarafa Group" />
           <tab class="zarafamailgroup" name="Zarafa Mail group" />
           ...
     </grouptabs>
...

